HEADWORD: Goatfish
<hw>Goat"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A fish of the genus <gen>Upeneus</gen>, inhabiting the Gulf of
